Description: An implementation of the "Design Analysis" proposed by 
    Gelman and Carlin (2014). It combines the evaluation of Power-Analysis 
    with other inferential-risks as Type-M error (e.g. Magnitude) and Type-S
    error (e.g. Sign). See also Altoè et al. (2020) and Bertoldo et al. (2020).
